      "output": "<path>C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\Documents\\agentsong\\docs\\standards\\adrs\\adr-012-intrinsic-before-extrinsic.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # ADR-012: Intrinsic Before Extrinsic\n2: \n3: **Status:** Proposed\n4: **Date:** 05 July 2026\n5: **Author:** Andrea Enning\n\n(Showing lines 1-5 of 91. Use offset=6 to continue.)\n</content>",
