      "output": "<path>C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\Documents\\agentsong\\SOPs\\SOP-004-Exporting-AI-Sessions.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # SOP-004: Exporting AI Sessions\n2: \n3: **Version:** 1.0  \n4: **Date:** 05 July 2026  \n5: **Author:** Andrea Enning (AndieKobbieTech)\n6: \n7: ---\n8: \n9: ## Purpose\n10: \n11: This SOP describes how to export AI coding sessions from various tools (opencode, MiniMax, Antigravity IDE, Chrome DevTools) into AgentSON format for search, backup, and cross-tool hydration.\n12: \n13: ---\n14: \n15: ## Prerequisites\n16: \n17: | Item | Requirement |\n18: |------|-------------|\n19: | **Software** | Python 3.12.3, AgentSON CLI |\n20: | **Data** | Existing AI sessions in supported tools |\n21: | **Location** | `~/agentson` |\n22: \n23: ---\n24: \n25: ## Supported Tools\n26: \n27: | Tool | Database Location |\n28: |------|-------------------|\n29: | opencode | `~\\.local\\share\\opencode\\opencode.db` |\n30: | MiniMax | `~\\.minimax\\sqlite.db` |\n31: | Antigravity IDE | `~\\.gemini\\antigravity-ide\\conversations\\*.db` |\n32: | Chrome DevTools | Export from Chrome DevTools AI Assistance panel (Markdown export) |\n33: \n34: ---\n35: \n36: ## Procedure\n37: \n38: ### Step 1: List Available Sessions\n39: \n40: ```powershell\n41: cd ~/agentson\n42: \n43: # List opencode sessions\n44: python -m cli.main list --tool opencode\n45: \n46: # List MiniMax sessions\n47: python -m cli.main list --tool minimax\n48: \n49: # List Antigravity sessions\n50: python -m cli.main list --tool antigravity\n51: ```\n52: \n53: ### Step 2: Export Specific Session\n54: \n55: ```powershell\n56: # Export specific opencode session\n57: python -m cli.main export --tool opencode --session ses_xxx --output \"~/Downloads\"\n58: \n59: # Export specific MiniMax session\n60: python -m cli.main export --tool minimax --session xxx --output \"~/Downloads\"\n61: ```\n62: \n63: ### Step 3: Export All Sessions\n64: \n65: ```powershell\n66: # Export all opencode sessions\n67: python -m cli.main export --tool opencode --all --output \"~/Downloads\"\n68: \n69: # Export all MiniMax sessions\n70: python -m cli.main export --tool minimax --all --output \"~/Downloads\"\n71: ```\n72: \n73: ---\n74: \n75: ## Output\n76: \n77: | Tool | File Pattern |\n78: |------|--------------|\n79: | opencode | `opencode_ses_xxx.AgentSON` |\n80: | MiniMax | `minimax_xxx.AgentSON` |\n81: | Antigravity | `antigravity_xxx.AgentSON` |\n82: \n83: ---\n84: \n85: ## Next Steps\n86: \n87: After exporting, proceed to:\n88: - **SOP-003**: View sessions in browser\n89: - **SOP-005**: Search sessions for specific content\n\n(End of file - total 89 lines)\n</content>",
